Demonstrates how to export a Chart to an PNG image or a PDF file using Inkscape.

Requires Inkscape to operate. Free download available at:
http://inkscape.org/download/?lang=en

Inkscape tutorial with full list of export options is available at:
http://tavmjong.free.fr/INKSCAPE/MANUAL/html/CommandLine-Export.html

Note that ASP.NET MVC and Inkscape are chosen just as an example.
The same approach can be used for different server platforms and SVG processing software.
